{"tid":2014321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 尋幽探秘] 救世軍葵涌女童院舊址申建安老院舍　擬保留主樓及小教堂","createTime":"2020-05-13T03:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T03:15:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"507a88416b648c58cb2365945cf007def529807b","tid":2014321,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259048/org/842d7bca683366621af10ff057219e4e.jpg/6n2Kc0c9doPEfeWscCzf7OVms6AJqaHEQ-dt_kPnbf4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259048%2Forg%2F842d7bca683366621af10ff057219e4e.jpg%2F6n2Kc0c9doPEfeWscCzf7OVms6AJqaHEQ-dt_kPnbf4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=eeee777b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://peacesail.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/1966-kwai-chung-captioned2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeacesail.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F08%2F1966-kwai-chung-captioned2.jpg&h=70550569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救世軍葵涌女童院位於葵涌梨木道1號，據新業主向城規會提交資料，該地段的主大樓於1941年落成，1971至 1994年間為葵涌救世軍女童院，之後一直荒廢近四分之一世紀。<br />\n <img src=\"https://peacesail.files.wordpress.com/2018/08/tsakcc-1955-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeacesail.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F08%2Ftsakcc-1955-2.jpg&h=40827bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259058/org/53eb4a37dae552a44ada4b7f415a6e81.jpg/YRouyWCI3NCj2QjwX8EdgcIDb1x1ZzctHFmDehxZg3o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259058%2Forg%2F53eb4a37dae552a44ada4b7f415a6e81.jpg%2FYRouyWCI3NCj2QjwX8EdgcIDb1x1ZzctHFmDehxZg3o&h=71d84d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救世軍女童院的主大樓為一幢三層高、具西方建築特色的「古堡式」建築物，其他構築物則為 1-2 層高。據保育團體「香港隅地」提供的相片，這幢建築物有古堡式的外牆內，並有水磨石製造的角形旋轉樓梯。旋梯的採光設計巧妙，無論從頂層俯視，還是從地面大廳上望，都構成漂亮圖形。不過，女童院雖然歷史悠久，但並非歷史建築物，未曾獲古諮會評級。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ruwmc_Ky6c4/W0K6NXAhwmI/AAAAAAAIOAw/ZidILz926q4Op6u93siEYGeRzDSQJOz2ACKgBGAs/s640/1955%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%2588%2590%2B-%2B%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E9%259A%258A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ruwmc_Ky6c4%2FW0K6NXAhwmI%2FAAAAAAAIOAw%2FZidILz926q4Op6u93siEYGeRzDSQJOz2ACKgBGAs%2Fs640%2F1955%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E8%252590%2525BD%2525E6%252588%252590%252B-%252B%2525E6%252595%252591%2525E4%2525B8%252596%2525E8%2525BB%25258D%2525E8%252591%2525B5%2525E6%2525B6%25258C%2525E9%25259A%25258A.jpg&h=d3e74475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259055/org/fe73eb52d0b7070e75320690e143c2af.jpg/SjZo4FgMad8fmOlSf9JrhuUIH8ZkwzGusO_w6LDv8Og\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259055%2Forg%2Ffe73eb52d0b7070e75320690e143c2af.jpg%2FSjZo4FgMad8fmOlSf9JrhuUIH8ZkwzGusO_w6LDv8Og&h=5a25fb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新業主指，自 2018 年 4 月成為業主，現希望發展為安老院舍，由「休憩用地」改劃為「政府、機構或社區」地帶。擬議發展的總發展地盤面積約為 10,888 平方米，佔整個「休憩用地」地帶(12,435平方米)的 88%，而其餘座落該地帶的土地為政府土地。新業主指，大部份建築物均甚破舊，而申請地點亦從來沒有開放給公眾人士作休憩用地，故現希望發展為安老院舍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GXGvqUlYOa0/W0K6NeE-t7I/AAAAAAAIOAw/IkLvhTcFrTkyEwhpzitqUMiSRDPC6i5gQCKgBGAs/s400/%25E6%259C%258978%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-GXGvqUlYOa0%2FW0K6NeE-t7I%2FAAAAAAAIOAw%2FIkLvhTcFrTkyEwhpzitqUMiSRDPC6i5gQCKgBGAs%2Fs400%2F%2525E6%25259C%25258978%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E6%2525AD%2525B7%2525E5%25258F%2525B2%2525E4%2525B9%25258B%2525E6%252595%252591%2525E4%2525B8%252596%2525E8%2525BB%25258D%2525E8%252591%2525B5%2525E6%2525B6%25258C%2525E5%2525A5%2525B3%2525E7%2525AB%2525A5%2525E9%252599%2525A2-%2525E6%2525AD%2525B7%2525E5%25258F%2525B2%2525E7%252585%2525A7%2525E7%252589%252587.jpg&h=38eafc1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259051/org/2bb1fea929c1dca91c4a53ae3bb4ddab.jpg/VA-JrT1m7f_WROK6QJATNNaIbwEXsTFR4jBxNeIwcTU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259051%2Forg%2F2bb1fea929c1dca91c4a53ae3bb4ddab.jpg%2FVA-JrT1m7f_WROK6QJATNNaIbwEXsTFR4jBxNeIwcTU&h=9bd38981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259057/org/871781e8ea28d0f4d9678d345067f258.jpg/iGo8q-MMwLlDmbJU4fD8GkEJE9R_mJOp-UBEXvlARF4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259057%2Forg%2F871781e8ea28d0f4d9678d345067f258.jpg%2FiGo8q-MMwLlDmbJU4fD8GkEJE9R_mJOp-UBEXvlARF4&h=0646581d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n料提供140個床位<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-5S4G9PrVIJE/W0n0UKrjBMI/AAAAAAAIONI/Ajlw-qtJ8J4Rx0nPqgevJenKne1iBOFuwCKgBGAs/s1600/%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580%2B2018%25E5%25B9%25B47%25E6%259C%25889%25E6%2597%25A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-5S4G9PrVIJE%2FW0n0UKrjBMI%2FAAAAAAAIONI%2FAjlw-qtJ8J4Rx0nPqgevJenKne1iBOFuwCKgBGAs%2Fs1600%2F%2525E9%252580%252599%2525E5%252580%25258B%2525E5%25259F%2525BA%2525E7%25259F%2525B3%2525E5%2525B7%2525B2%2525E7%2525B6%252593%2525E8%2525A2%2525AB%2525E6%2525AF%252580%252B2018%2525E5%2525B9%2525B47%2525E6%25259C%2525889%2525E6%252597%2525A5.jpg&h=19cf8d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新業主指，為尊重申請地點過去的歷史，女童院的主大樓及小教堂將會保留及活化。擬建安老院舍將提供 140 個床位，人均宿位面積約 7.5 平方米，比社會福利署 2017 年的標準(6.5 平方米)為高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259059/org/c5b455ea201ce37eb8caed4b962051eb.jpg/xw7GG1dh8W0m1lBK3f2u5_XTHEm3xBjK0QtRR9ELUUc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259059%2Forg%2Fc5b455ea201ce37eb8caed4b962051eb.jpg%2Fxw7GG1dh8W0m1lBK3f2u5_XTHEm3xBjK0QtRR9ELUUc&h=8296ec7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擬建安老院宿位主要向內園，以增加與現有道路的分隔距離，從而減低噪音影響。為提供休憩空間予公眾人士享用，申請地點將提供公共休憩空間。為利用是次發展機會擴大休憩空間，擬建安老院內的庭園亦設私人花園。整個項目預計於 2025 年落成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3259070/org/d4a2d67621780964d49d55c1cb660c6f.png/JXwepbFpU1f5Xev1H1Vk-TUty2ZSGjzz4QzFKuEMxSo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3259070%2Forg%2Fd4a2d67621780964d49d55c1cb660c6f.png%2FJXwepbFpU1f5Xev1H1Vk-TUty2ZSGjzz4QzFKuEMxSo&h=3d84f57b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}